cs.CL, cs.IR, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.NE

This paper is about a natural language processing task, specifically Vietnamese word segmentation. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CL (Computation and Language). The paper also uses machine learning techniques, which could fall under categories such as cs.IR (Information Retrieval), cs.LG (Machine Learning), and cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). Finally, the paper discusses performance speed, which could fall under cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing).
